==File Format== The following file extensions are specific to SmartDraw: *.SDR – “SmartDraw Documents,” a binary file format used for saving SmartDraw documents. *.SDT – “Smart/Draw Templates,” a binary file format used for saving SmartDraw reusable document templates. *.SDL – “SmartDraw Libraries,” a binary file format used for saving symbol libraries in SmartDraw. *.SCZ - "SmartDraw Collections," a binary file format used for saving SmartDraw collections.
